Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.37,0:00:06.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:22.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.83,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.30,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:36.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the\nair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:43.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:52.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:59.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:06.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:13.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:26.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Our house is all fixed now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:55.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! So this is the\nfull power of a goddess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:17.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You actually restored our house\nand the whole city in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:20.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did cause everyone\na lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Lord of Terror\nis no longer a threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:30.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my power is too great, so I'm\ngoing to have to seal it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:51.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. I guess Urd's playing\ntag with Skuld again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:55.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the first thing she does\nthe minute her license is reinstated...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you cornered, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck is...{\i0}\nI've got you cornered, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:01.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,U...Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:16.16,AMG next episode name blue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Urd's Little Romance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:20.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...slippery-smooth\nand totally flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why'd she turn into a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:29.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To live in this world, we goddesses\nmust draw on an energy supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from Yggdrasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The system crashed during the\NLord of Terror incident, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:42.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In Urd's case, I think that's how the\nenergy deficiency manifested itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:47.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So if she keeps on using her powers,\nshe's only going to get smaller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:52.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, we goddesses have alternate\nenergy sources for emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alternate energy source?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the heck with you! Goshdarnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess...could it be sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In Big Sister's case, it's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:14.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She did use her full power\njust now to fix the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\nyou seem fine, Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, because she has\nno powers to speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The grownups are talking right now, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But listen, Urd,\nI'll play with you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've really got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a good idea, using your powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we do\nsomething about your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what kind of clothes should we\nbuy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:49.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know, we can get her something\nat the neighborhood thrift shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To conserve energy,\nI've split off from myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go get\nsome clothes for Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Urd's Castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I think it rather becomes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean she actually likes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine!{\i0}\nI'm going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's really cool! Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...my cram school class\nhas been canceled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I always hang out here...\nit's just a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sake's not for children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's not sake,\nit's a video game...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:00.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you've got it all wrong.\nI told you, I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking sake in broad daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are\nyour parents thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they do like to take\nthe hands-off approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me? I'm NOT a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang onto this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh...um...{\i0}\nIs she a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, rats. I just used up\nall my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:55.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was nice enough to bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But in any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:01.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:19.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Nothing like a drink\nafter a hard day's work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But really, you're a\nlittle pushover, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Running away with me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, but, isn't that why\nyou were able to get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were you\ndoing just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:49.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was ditching cram school.\NThere's no class today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}\nI'm talking about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one that\njust came out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...how do you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Button A, and this is Button B.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the Start button,\nand here's Reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:08.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure.{\i0}\NWant to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:11.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all right.{\i0}\NHere are the instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a System Administrator goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:25.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:26.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}\nI'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...try this one next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had a pretty good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way...how could you beat them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think I'll head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shohei Yoshida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:31.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...um...Uru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey! Will you be here tomorrow,\ntoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really going to be late\nfor cram school, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome home, Urd!{\i0}\NWelcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Great news, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:47.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, we heard from the Almighty\nafter you left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From the Almighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He told us that we should use\nmoon rocks as an alternate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...energy source until\nthe system gets restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, they would definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:02.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...how are we going to\nget our hands on moon rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:06.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out to make some.\NThe facilities we need are at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to\ngather up the materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, you only have to\nhold on a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no rush, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:18.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Being a kid is more fun than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, she does!{\i0}\NShe seems to be enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:04.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today I've got some games that are\nway more difficult than yesterday's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A volcano, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:22.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:27.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moon rocks are mainly composed of\na type of volcanic rock called basalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:29.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So all we need is to get some basalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:34.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Moon rocks have a slightly\ndifferent composition than Earth rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to\nmake them ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:41.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But once we do that, you two\ncan go back to normal right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Going to all this trouble for us...\nI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is the one thing\nI can do for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...so...wiped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even I'm not that out of breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:04.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me some sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um! But listen, I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:17.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see...um...you can't drink\nsake until you're an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still in grammar school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:24.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And even if it's a vending machine,\nI still shouldn't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:28.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...\nI don't think I can...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Falling down isn't my thing, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You can do it, Shohei!\NYou're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And don't look up, got that?\NDon't look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:16.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Most\npeople would say ''Don't look down!''
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rats, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why\nI told you not to look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:42.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I just got even smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing, just talking to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:59.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't buy\nyour sake for you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for cram school,\nso I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still light out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got early classes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:10.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:20.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can't do something,\nyou'll never be able to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how easy it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...hey, wait! Hold on, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's open! Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? Go? Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to climb it,\nwhat did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do now\nis cross over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:28.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way can I do that!\nIf I fall, I'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then just don't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can't do something,\nyou'll never be able to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how easy it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, saying that is one thing...\nif I really do fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you did it yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My sake...you brought\nit to me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:10.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I able to do\nsomething like that then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right...I've got to go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:04.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, from up there, this was\nthe tallest building I could find...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, nothing! Forget it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:17.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might've\ngotten too involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be heading\nfor your cram school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:25.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll see you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are a foreigner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to be in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:47.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you when we met, remember?\NThat I'm not a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, they're done! The moon rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:07.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn back to your old self now.\nIsn't this wonderful, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait...until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, so he did follow me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, don't tell me\nthat you and that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:34.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was just passing the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess I did something\nthat I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:44.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's best that\nI turn back now, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}TARIKI HONGAN TEMPLE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?\N{\i1}TARIKI HONGAN TEMPLE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...are you a friend of\nmy little sister's, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you came to see Urd,\nshe's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She went back to her own home, you\nsee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she probably won't\nbe coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:40.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:41.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\NThat's not why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:51.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please give\nthis back to Urd for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Also, tell Urd that I said thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:59.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm going to stop\ngiving up before I even try...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That I know I can hang in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:04.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And so, when I'm all grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...can we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:20.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So grow up fast, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:09.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SKULD LABORATORY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:22.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AUGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.15,AMG to be cont,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}TO BE CONTINUED{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:25.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:35.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:40.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:45.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:56.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:23:01.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:06.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:17.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:22.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:28.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:33.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:38.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:44.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:49.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:54.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
